# providers/
#
# React context providers that wrap the application tree.
# These are "use client" components registered in the root layout.
#
# Examples (to be created during migration phases):
#   providers/query-provider.tsx    ← TanStack QueryClientProvider wrapper
#   providers/tooltip-provider.tsx  ← Radix TooltipProvider wrapper
#   providers/theme-provider.tsx    ← next-themes ThemeProvider (if dark mode is needed)
#   providers/index.tsx             ← Composite provider that wraps all of the above
